Dry
Four outputs for electric locking hardware, powered by an external
power supply. Each output is rated up to 2A/3OVDC and 0.5A/125VAC.
COMING SOON Digital Inputs (DII, DI2 , DI3)
Three digital inputs, programmable for request-to-exit or door-state-
sensor devices (such as a push-to-exit button or motion sensor).
COMING SOON Wiegand Reader Port (WIGI, WIG2)
Two, three-wire Wiegand ports. For use in existing systems where third -
party Wiegand readers are required at the Intercom's location: Replaces
existing Wiegand readers and connects directly to third-party access
control systems:
